allorsProductCategory.name: SPECIAL AIRPORT TRUCKS
allorsProductCategory.description:
If you look through the windows of an airport terminal, you will often see these special airport vehicles like:  water truck, toilet truck, catering truck, deicer, ambulift, fuel truck, cargo truck, fire truck, snow plowing , sweeping vehicles.
They perform special tasks on airports around the globe. Thanks to the latest safety procedures special airport vehicles are active on many fronts in order to allow smooth operations, safe runaway and maintenance of the airport infrastructure.
